<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; }
    h1 { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    h2 { color: #2980b9; margin-top: 30px; border-left: 5px solid #3498db; padding-left: 10px; }
    h3 { color: #16a085; margin-top: 25px; }
    h4 { color: #e67e22; margin-top: 20px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 12px; text-align: left; }
    th { background-color: #f8f9fa; font-weight: bold; }
    ul { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 50px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #7f8c8d; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header-box { background: #fdfdfd; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-box">
        <h1>HRFlow: Enterprise HRMS & AI Automation System</h1>
        <p><strong>Comprehensive Application Summary & Technical Documentation</strong></p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
    <p><b>HRFlow</b> is a state-of-the-art Human Resource Management System (HRMS) designed to revolutionize personnel management through AI-driven workforce optimization. The platform features a sophisticated multi-departmental architecture that enables real-time monitoring, automated workflow processing, and advanced behavioral analytics across diverse organizational roles.</p>

    <h2>2. Technical Architecture & Stack</h2>
    <p>The application leverages a high-performance, modern tech stack designed for real-time data flow and scalable AI processing.</p>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Layer</th>
                <th>Technology</th>
                <th>Implementation Detail</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Frontend</b></td>
                <td>HTML5, Vanilla CSS, JavaScript (ES6+)</td>
                <td>Glassmorphic UI design with real-time DOM updates.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Backend API</b></td>
                <td>Node.js, Express.js</td>
                <td>Scalable REST API for user management and data routing.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Cloud Infrastructure</b></td>
                <td>Google Firebase (Firestore & Auth)</td>
                <td>Real-time NoSQL synchronization and secure authentication.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>AI Engine</b></td>
                <td>Python, Scikit-Learn, Pandas</td>
                <td>Predictive modeling and behavioral anomaly detection.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><b>Activity Tracking</b></td>
                <td>Custom JS Telemetry Engine</td>
                <td>Non-intrusive tracking of active/idle time and tab-switching.</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>3. Key Functional Modules</h2>

    <h3>A. Multi-Role Management Dashboards</h3>
    <p>HRFlow provides specialized portals tailored to specific management needs:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Sales Manager:</b> Real-time tracking of revenue targets and lead conversion.</li>
        <li><b>Marketing Manager:</b> Campaign ROI visualization and integrated notification hubs.</li>
        <li><b>Engineering Manager:</b> Technical KPI tracking and agile sprint progress monitoring.</li>
        <li><b>Operations Manager:</b> Budgetary oversight and resource allocation tools.</li>
        <li><b>HR Manager:</b> Personnel management, onboarding, and global policy control.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>B. AI Command Center & Behavioral Analytics</h3>
    <p>A dedicated AI engine monitors workforce health and engagement:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Behavioral ML:</b> Uses Decision Trees to classify work habits (Focused vs. Distracted).</li>
        <li><b>Anomaly Detection:</b> Flags unusual work patterns using Isolation Forest algorithms.</li>
        <li><b>Productivity Scoring:</b> Quantifies daily performance based on real-time telemetry.</li>
        <li><b>Distraction Alerts:</b> Notifies managers of potential social media or external distractions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>C. Employee Self-Service Ecosystem</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Workflows:</b> Automated leave request and task approval systems.</li>
        <li><b>Task Boards:</b> Visualized personal task management for daily operations.</li>
        <li><b>Communications:</b> Premium notification center for real-time internal updates.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>D. Enterprise Command Center (TVC)</h3>
    <p>A high-level dashboard designed for executive leadership, providing a 360-degree view of organizational productivity and system health.</p>

    <h2>4. Recent Enhancements</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Advanced Tab-Switching Detection:</b> Hardened security to track off-site activity accurately.</li>
        <li><b>Mock-Data Architecture:</b> Transitioned to high-performance standalone prototypes for seamless demos.</li>
        <li><b>Departmental Routing:</b> Intelligent logic to ensure notifications reach the correct managers instantly.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Prepared by <b>Antigravity AI</b><br>
        <i>Enterprise Solutions Group</i><br>
        Document Generated: May 4, 2026</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
